(126, 2, 'ASCOLL', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, ''Trebuchet MS'', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;“The company you are about to get to know owes it success to a number of, what I consider to be, fundamental values: innovation; the fundamental importance of people; team work and informal relationships. These elements have all enabled Askoll to develop into an international group with operating units in Italy and all over the world in just thirty years. Our group now has sales of Euro almost 500 million. We plough back more than 6% of our sales into research and development. This means we can add value to our products. It makes us the architects and masters of innovative technologies. It means we can enhance the quality of our work and the skill of our people. We have revolutionised the world of aquariology, household appliances and heating. We are set to take on the new, winning challenges of the future. ”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', ''),
(126, 1, 'ASCOLL', '&lt;h1 style=&quot;font-size: 29px; margin: 0px 0px 0.1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Итальянская фирма Askoll.&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0.1em; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Компания Askoll - это безусловно мировой лидер в сегменте производства насосов.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0.1em; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Почему Askoll лидер? Потому что она производит насосы для практически всех стиральных машин. Технология производства и поставок выделили эти насосы как самые недорогие, а по надёжности и износоустойчивости на высшем уровне. Насосы Askoll &amp;nbsp;имеют высокую мощность, что делает их более тихими и эффективными в работе. Эти насосы - результат гениального инженерного решения! Поставил и забыл! Именно за это его так любят мастера.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0.1em; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Любопытно что такие производители-гиганты как Bosch, Ariston, Samsung и др. не занимаются производством насосов, а делают заказы именно в компании Askoll. Разберите свою машинку, и убедитесь сами.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0.1em; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Насосы Askoll используют такие брэнды как:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0.1em; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Samsung, Ariston, Asko, Bosch, Lg, Candy, Electrolux, Zanussi, Gorenje, Hansa, Indesit, Kaiser, Rolsen, Ardo, Siemens, Whirlpool, General Electric, Zerowatt&amp;nbsp; и др.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', ''),
(126, 3, 'ASCOLL', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, ''Trebuchet MS'', verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;“The company you are about to get to know owes it success to a number of, what I consider to be, fundamental values: innovation; the fundamental importance of people; team work and informal relationships. These elements have all enabled Askoll to develop into an international group with operating units in Italy and all over the world in just thirty years. Our group now has sales of Euro almost 500 million. We plough back more than 6% of our sales into research and development. This means we can add value to our products. It makes us the architects and masters of innovative technologies. It means we can enhance the quality of our work and the skill of our people. We have revolutionised the world of aquariology, household appliances and heating. We are set to take on the new, winning challenges of the future. ”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', 'ASCOLL', ''),
(127, 2, 'BOILERNOVA', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;&quot;&gt;Boilernova is a young company, founded in 2004, yet backed by the more than twenty year experience of its founding partners in the heating business, specifically storage cylinders and tanks.The company’s headquarters are in Zevio, Verona province (Italy). At Boilernova we design, manufacture and market several different ranges of storage cylinders, offering a wide choice in terms of sizes, storage capacity, installation and suitability for use in mixed systems with solar heating panels and other sources of renewable energy. If the product ranges available in the catalogue do not fully respond to the specific need, we can design and develop a product “to measure”, so as to satisfy any customer requirement. Fast and reliable delivery times are among our main objectives, achieved by continuously updated production planning and an extremely vertical manufacturing process (everything is made in-house), ensuring a highly flexible system.Constant research into new technologies, the professionalism acquired and development of know-how means we can satisfy the needs of leading companies in the heating and air-conditioning sectors, providing a compete outsourced production cycle and specific Boilernova processing methods for the construction of the required products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', ''),
(127, 1, 'BOILERNOVA', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;&quot;&gt;Boilernova is a young company, founded in 2004, yet backed by the more than twenty year experience of its founding partners in the heating business, specifically storage cylinders and tanks.The company’s headquarters are in Zevio, Verona province (Italy). At Boilernova we design, manufacture and market several different ranges of storage cylinders, offering a wide choice in terms of sizes, storage capacity, installation and suitability for use in mixed systems with solar heating panels and other sources of renewable energy. If the product ranges available in the catalogue do not fully respond to the specific need, we can design and develop a product “to measure”, so as to satisfy any customer requirement. Fast and reliable delivery times are among our main objectives, achieved by continuously updated production planning and an extremely vertical manufacturing process (everything is made in-house), ensuring a highly flexible system.Constant research into new technologies, the professionalism acquired and development of know-how means we can satisfy the needs of leading companies in the heating and air-conditioning sectors, providing a compete outsourced production cycle and specific Boilernova processing methods for the construction of the required products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', ''),
(127, 3, 'BOILERNOVA', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; width: 870px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;&quot;&gt;Boilernova ist ein junges, 2004 gegründetes Unternehmen, das aus der über zwanzigjährigen Erfahrung seiner Gesellschafter im Bereich der Heiztechnik und insbesondere der Boiler und Tanks entstanden ist. Der Hauptsitz des Unternehmens befindet sich in Zevio, in der Provinz von Verona (Italien).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; width: 870px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px;&quot;&gt;Boilernova plant, baut und vertreibt ein breit gefächertes Angebot verschiedener Boilertypen, deren Abmessungen, Speicherkapazität, Installation und Anpassungsfähigkeit zur Verwendung in gemischten Heizungsanlagen (Solarenergie und erneuerbare Energiequellen im Allgemeinen) stets die richtige Wahl für jede Einsatzbedingung gestatten. Sollte die im Katalog enthaltene Auswahl den jeweiligen spezifischen Anforderungen nicht voll entsprechen, ist das Unternehmen in der Lage, ein Produkt „nach Maß“ zu planen und zu bauen und immer jede Kundenanforderung zu erfüllen. Kurze, zuverlässige Lieferfristen gehören zu den Hauptzielen, die wir uns gesetzt haben, und die wir über eine laufend aktualisierte Programmierung und einen extrem vertikalisierten Fertigungsprozess (wir fertigen alles intern) verfolgen, was eine große Flexibilität des Systems ermöglicht. Dank konstanter Erforschung neuer Technologien und auf jahrelanger Erfahrung beruhender Professionalität sowie ständiger Weiterentwicklung unseres Know-hows sind wir in der Lage, die Anforderungen der wichtigsten Unternehmen im Bereich der Heiz- und Klimatechnik zu erfüllen und ihnen für die Entwicklung und Fertigung spezifischer Produkte auf Anfrage den gesamten Produktionszyklus und die Bearbeitungstechnologie von Boilernova zur Verfügung zu stellen. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', 'BOILERNOVA', ''),
